text: The Catalan Wikipedia () is the Catalan-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition was started in March 2001, and is the fourth-oldest edition of Wikipedia. It is the 17th largest edition by article count. As of May 2013, it had over 400,000 articles.:ca:Especial:Estad√≠stiques As of March 11, 2016, the number of the Catalan Wikipedia's articles reached 500,000. == References == == Other websites == * Catalan Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2001
